&lt;p&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;runtime&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Fix TaskExecutionState against non-serializable exceptions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;commit 9b9594a7569ed01dcfc97a82880938c033171bec&lt;br/&gt;
Author: Stephan Ewen &amp;lt;sewen@apache.org&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Date:   2015-05-03T02:41:03Z&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1672&quot; title=&quot;Refactor task registration/unregistration&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-1672&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-1672&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;runtime&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Unify Task and RuntimeEnvironment into one class.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;This simplifies and hardens the failure handling during task startup&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Guarantees that no actor system threads are blocked by task bootstrap, or task canceling&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Corrects some previously erroneous corner case state transitions&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Adds simple and robust tests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


